  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3 \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc8 \u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc6\u0ba9 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc2\u0baa\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0ba4\u0bc1 - \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0ba9\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "What we have mentioned that the emergency law will affect the Sinhalese people is now proven - Chanakian",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Government leaders should at least pay attention to solving the basic political problems of the Tamil people. The Tamil National Federation member Sanakyan told the Rajamanikam Sabha that the Emergency Act and its accompanying arrests are nothing new for Tamils, and what we have mentioned that the Emergency Act will affect the Sinhalese people is now true.",
        "He mentioned the above during the debate on the Emergency Act in Parliament today, Wednesday.",
        "Political leaders have had many opportunities to correct mistakes in Sri Lanka's political history, but they have not used them properly. That is also seen as a factor in the current economic crisis.",
        "The current leaders should correct the historical mistake and focus on economic progress.",
        "If the basic political problems of the Tamil people are resolved, then the economic crisis can be solved unanimously.",
        "If we establish special economic zones in the northern and eastern provinces, we can get the investments of the diaspora organizations in the best way.",
        ", the heads of state should pay special attention to solving the basic problems including the issue of dispossessed persons, release of Tamil political prisoners in jail, land release, etc.",
        "The youth involved in the struggle are being done now. Instead of arresting those involved in the struggle for better change and those involved in the struggle, pay attention to the arrest of those who manipulated the Central Bank, those who looted through the Chinese tax, those who set fire to the house of President Ranil Wickremesinghe and the houses of members of Parliament.",
        "Emergency law, arrests, etc. are nothing new to the Tamil people, instead of suppressing those involved in the struggle through the law, attention should be paid to fulfilling their legitimate demands. The protesters are expecting a constitutional change. The government should act democratically to implement them, he said."
      ],
